047200******************************************************************
047300*
047400 010-E-INICIO.
047500
047600
047700
047800     MOVE    ATTRIBUTE NAME OF ATTRIBUTE EXCEPTIONTASK
047900                            OF ATTRIBUTE EXCEPTIONTASK OF MYSELF
048000                            TO LINKTOCOMS.
048100
048200
048300     CHANGE  ATTRIBUTE TITLE OF "DCILIBRARY" TO LINKTOCOMS.
048400
048500
048600     ENABLE  INPUT   COMS-IN         KEY     "ONLINE"
048700
048800     CALL    "GET_DESIGNATOR_USING_NAME  IN  DCILIBRARY"
048900                                     USING   AX-AGENDA-OUT,
049000                                     VALUE   AGENDA,
049100                                             AX-AGENDA-DESG
049200                                     GIVING  AX-CALL-ERROR.
049300
049400
049500
049600
