049800       ON    EXCEPTION
049900             DISPLAY "PC/GEV/T446/DB : OPEN ERROR TDBDETRAN"
050000             PERFORM 140-E-ERRODB    THRU    140-S-ERRODB
050100             CALL    SYSTEM          DMTERMINATE.
050200
050300
050400     OPEN    INQUIRY    DB02
050500       ON    EXCEPTION
050600             DISPLAY "PC/GEV/T446/DB : OPEN ERROR TDBTAXAS"
050700             PERFORM 140-E-ERRODB    THRU    140-S-ERRODB
050800             CALL    SYSTEM          DMTERMINATE.
050900
051000
051100
051200
