052000*
052100 020-E-PROCESSA.
052200
052300
052400
052500     MOVE    SPACES                  TO      AREA-IN
052600                                             AREA-OUT.
052700
052800     RECEIVE COMS-IN MESSAGE         INTO    AREA-IN.
052900
053000     IF      COMS-IN-STATUS          =       00 OR 89 OR 92 OR
053100                                             93 OR 97
053200             NEXT    SENTENCE
053300     ELSE
053400     IF      COMS-IN-STATUS          =       99
053500             GO                      TO      020-S-PROCESSA
053600     ELSE
