054400                                     USING   USER-DESG
054500                                             USER-NAME
054600                                     GIVING  USER-FLAG.
054700
054800
054900
055000
055100
055200
055300
055400     IF      IN-CODE                 =       "V446"
055500             PERFORM 030-E-V446      THRU    030-S-V446
055600     ELSE
055700             MOVE    239             TO      IA1.
055800
055900
056000     MOVE    165                     TO      AX-LENGTH.
056100
