061900
062000     IF      (IN-CHASSI              =       SPACES     OR
062100                                             ZEROS      OR
062200                                             LOW-VALUES )
062300             MOVE    002             TO      IA1
062400             GO                      TO      040-S-VERIF-IN.
062500
062600
062700     MOVE    IN-CHASSI               TO     CH-CHASSI.
062800
063700*==>  VERIFICAR DIGITO CHECK DE CPF/CNPJ  PROPRIETARIO
063800
063900     IF      IN-CNPJ-PROP-X          =       ZEROS      OR
064000                                             SPACES     OR
064100                                             LOW-VALUES
064200             MOVE    003             TO      IA1
064300             GO                      TO      040-S-VERIF-IN.
