074300
074400
074500
074600     MOVE    "N"                     TO      CH-NOTFOUND.
074620
074640 060-LER-FIND-TAXAS.
074700
074800     FIND    NEXT TAXCPFSS1          AT
074900             TAX-SITUACAO            =      ZEROS           AND
075000             TAX-CPF-CGC             =      IN-CNPJ-PROP    AND
075100             TAX-COD-PAG             =      IN-COD-PAGTO
075200       ON    EXCEPTION
075300        IF   DMSTATUS (NOTFOUND)
075400             MOVE    "S"             TO      CH-NOTFOUND
075405             IF      AX-PRIMVEZ      =       ZEROS
075450                     MOVE    463     TO      IA1
075500                     GO              060-S-FIND-TAXAS
075505             ELSE
075510                     MOVE    ZEROS   TO      IA1
075515                     GO              060-S-FIND-TAXAS
075600        ELSE
