075800             PERFORM 140-E-ERRODB    THRU    140-S-ERRODB
075900             CALL    SYSTEM          DMTERMINATE.
076000
076100*     ADD     1                       TO     IX1.
076110     ADD     1                       TO     OUT-QTDE-TAX.
076200
076300*     IF      IX1                     >      5
076305*             COMPUTE IX1  =          IX1   -   1
076400*             GO                      060-S-FIND-TAXAS.
